JOHANNESBURG - KFC has condemned a racial attack at one of its Pretoria outlets. A video has gone viral on social media showing a black couple being beaten up by six white men in Montana.The assault happened after the couple asked the men to move forward in the drive-through queue.VIDEO: Couple assaulted at KFC drive-through, video goes viralFour people have been arrested while two suspects remain at large.KFC says it's doing everything it can to help the authorities.It will wait for the police report before making further comments.eNCA